OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FMichael B Jordan paid tribute to past
OL,7,Fblack Oscar winners as he was named
OL,8,Fbest actor at the Academy Awards.
OL,10,FHe won the gong for his lead roles as
OL,11,Ftwins in vampire drama Sinners and
OL,12,Fsaid: "I stand here because of the
OL,13,Fpeople that came before me," and
OL,14,Fnamechecked Sidney Poitier, Denzel
OL,15,FWashington, Halle Berry, Jamie Foxx,
OL,16,FForest Whittaker and Will Smith.
OL,18,FAs he collected the prize he said:
OL,19,F"God is good," before addressing his
OL,20,Fmother and saying: "Mama, what's up?"
OL,26,@tD@GOUuD@\O]{D@AOU{D@NO]|D@TOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
