OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773630202
OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FHe continued: "Thank you, everybody in
OL,7,Fthis room and everybody at home for
OL,8,Fsupporting me over my career. I feel
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,F"I know you guys want me to do well
OL,12,Fand I want to do that because you guys
OL,13,Fbet on me.
OL,15,F"So thank you for keep betting on me,
OL,16,Fand I'm gonna keep stepping up, and
OL,17,FI'm gonna keep being the best version
OL,18,Fof myself I could be.
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773630202
OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,F"Thank you for everybody in this room
OL,7,Fthat has something to do with my
OL,8,Fsuccess.
OL,10,F"I love you guys and everybody at home
OL,11,Fwho supported Sinners, who went to go
OL,12,Fsee the movie, once, twice, three,
OL,13,Ffour or five times, thank you, because
OL,14,Fyou guys made this movie what it is. I
OL,15,Flove you. I love you. I love you."
OL,17,FEarlier in the ceremony Sean Penn won
OL,18,Fa third Oscar, but was not present at
OL,19,Fthe ceremony to collect his prize.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@bO]
