OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FHe won the best supporting actor gong
OL,7,Ffor his turn as racist military man
OL,8,FColonel Lockjaw in One Battle After
OL,9,FAnother.
OL,11,FHe defeated his co-star Benicio del
OL,12,FToro, Sinners star Delroy Lindo,
OL,13,FSentimental Value's Stellan Skarsgard
OL,14,Fand Frankenstein's Jacob Elordi, but
OL,15,Fwas not at the event in Los Angeles to
OL,16,Freceive the accolade.
OL,18,FPenn has previously won Oscars for his
OL,19,Fperformances in Mystic River and Milk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
