OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FKieran Culkin, who won the category
OL,7,Flast year for A Real Pain, announced
OL,8,FPenn's victory and said: "Sean Penn
OL,9,Fcouldn't be here tonight, or didn't
OL,10,Fwant to, so I will take this for him."
OL,12,FPenn was also absent from the Baftas
OL,13,Fand the Actor Awards, where he was
OL,14,Falso triumphant. He did attend the
OL,15,FGolden Globes, where he was defeated
OL,16,Fby Skarsgard in the category.
OL,18,FAmy Madigan won the first Oscar of the
OL,19,F2026 ceremony and paid tribute to her
OL,20,Fhusband Ed Harris as she collected her
OL,21,Fgong.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUrD@fO]
