OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FThe Field Of Dreams star collected the
OL,7,Fprize for her terrifying turn as Aunt
OL,8,FGladys in the horror film Weapons.
OL,10,FReferring to her husband of more than
OL,11,F40 years, she said: "The most
OL,12,Fimportant is my beloved Ed who's been
OL,13,Fwith me forever, and that's a long-ass
OL,14,Ftime, and none of this would mean
OL,15,Fanything if he wasn't by my side.
OL,17,FShe added: "Thank you, I'm very
OL,18,Foverwhelmed."
OL,26,@sD@UOUyD@LOUzD@MO]
