OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FRyan Coogler won the best original
OL,7,Fscreenplay Oscar for his vampire film
OL,8,FSinners, while Paul Thomas Anderson
OL,9,Fwon the best adapted screenplay for
OL,10,FOne Battle After Another.
OL,12,FAnderson was also named best director.
OL,14,FThere was a dramatic moment when there
OL,15,Fwas a tie in the live action short
OL,16,Fcategory, which was won by both Two
OL,17,FPeople Exchanging Saliva and The
OL,18,FSingers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
