OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FAfter the winners left the stage, host
OL,7,FConan O'Brien congratulated them and
OL,8,Fsaid: "You just ruined 22 million
OL,9,FOscar pools."
OL,11,FIt is the first time since 2013 there
OL,12,Fhave been tied winners, when Skyfall
OL,13,Fand Zero Dark Thirty shard the sound
OL,14,Fediting award.
OL,16,FComedian O'Brien, who is hosting the
OL,17,Fceremony for the second year in a row,
OL,18,Fopened the ceremony with an extended
OL,19,Fsketch dressed as Aunt Gladys, getting
OL,20,Fchased by children through scenes from
OL,21,Fthe films nominated for best picture.
OL,26,@pD@GOUqD@MO]
