OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FDressed in a red wig with heavy white
OL,7,Fmake up, like the antagonist from the
OL,8,Ffilm, he could be seen playing table
OL,9,Ftennis with Timothee Chalamet in Marty
OL,10,FSupreme, running across the stage of
OL,11,Fthe Globe in Hamnet, in the car with
OL,12,FBenicio del Toro in One Battle After
OL,13,FAnother and trying to get into the
OL,14,Fjuke joint in Sinners.
OL,16,FHe also made reference to the
OL,17,Fturbulent situation in the world at
OL,18,Fthe moment, when he said: "Last year
OL,19,Fwhen I hosted, Los Angeles was on
OL,20,Ffire. This year, everything is going
OL,21,Fgreat."
OL,26,@zD@[OU}D@GO]
