OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FHe also took a swipe at Timothee
OL,7,FChalamet's recent comment that "nobody
OL,8,Fcares" about opera and ballet, when he
OL,9,Fjoked: "I should tell you, security is
OL,10,Ftight tonight, I'm told there are
OL,11,Fconcerns about attacks from both the
OL,12,Fopera and ballet communities."
OL,14,FO'Brien pointed out it was the first
OL,15,Ftime since 2012 there were no British
OL,16,Flead acting nominees, and added: "A
OL,17,FBritish spokesperson said 'Yeah, at
OL,18,Fleast we arrest our paedophiles'."
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@FO]qD@HOUtD@^O]xD@bOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
