OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FO'Brien also acknowledged that these
OL,7,Fare "chaotic, frightening times,"
OL,8,Fadding: "It's at moments like these
OL,9,Fthat I believe the Oscars are
OL,10,Fparticularly resonant."
OL,12,FReferring to the number of countries
OL,13,Fand continents represented, he said
OL,14,Fthe nominated films are "the product
OL,15,Fof thousands of people speaking
OL,16,Fdifferent languages working hard to
OL,17,Fproduce something of beauty".
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@aO]pD@IOUrD@WO]vD@YOUyD@\O]
