OL,3,CMichael B Jordan pays tribute to other
OL,4,Cblack winners in emotional Oscar speech
OL,6,FHe added they show "global artistry,
OL,7,Fcollaboration, patience, resilience
OL,8,Fand that rarest of qualities,
OL,9,Foptimism."
OL,11,FBox office hit KPop Demon Hunters won
OL,12,Fthe best animated film prize, while
OL,13,FFrankenstein won the Oscar for best
OL,14,Fcostume design, as well as the Oscar
OL,15,Ffor make up and hair styling.
OL,26,@nD@TOUqD@JO]
